spect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/oZw0XF0DRrehnE4tkoqp8iPduZF.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":1.75}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T06:03:05.412+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":100,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.joydiv.org/jddoc.htm","overview":"A chronological account of the influential late 1970s English rock band."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En 1976, quatre jeunes hommes issus de la post-industrielle Manchester se rendent à un concert des Sex Pistols. Fortement inspirés par ce show auquel ils ont assisté, ils décident de monter un groupe, Joy Division. Près de 30 ans plus tard, malgré une tragédie qui les a arrêtés dans leur élan, Joy Division connaît un succès et une influence plus grande que jamais. Leur héritage résonne tout particulièrement dans une industrie musicale actuelle carriériste et une culture pop surmédiatisée. Grâce à des interviews des membres survivants du groupe, aujourd'hui réunis sous le nom de New Order, et à des archives inédites, Joy Division se fait la chronique d'un changement social et politique en Angleterre et nous entraîne dans l'histoire de ces quatre hommes, qui ont transcendé les barrières économiques et culturelles pour produire une musique atemporelle."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Joy Division","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Documental sobre la historia del famoso grupo británico Joy Division, rebautizado en 1980 como New Order, tras el suicidio de su cantante, Ian Curtis."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Joy Division - Die Dokumentation","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Die mittelenglische Stadt Manchester in den 70er Jahren: leere Fabrikhallen, Industriebrachen und Trostlosigkeit prägen das Stadtbild. Es ist eine Zeit der Rebellion, der Subkultur und des Punks. Nach einem Konzert der Sex Pistols im Jahr 1977 gründen vier junge Männer die Band Joy Division und machen mit ihren exzentrischen Auftritten schnell von sich Reden.\r Der Musikmanager Tony Wilson sagt einmal über die Band: \"Alle anderen Bands standen auf der Bühne, um Rockstars zu werden und im Showbusiness dabei zu sein. Nicht so Joy Division - sie hatten verdammt noch mal keine andere Wahl.\""},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Het verhaal van Joy Division en de dood van zanger Ian Curtis."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Joy Division","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"В 1976 году четверо молодых людей из разрушенного постиндустриального Манчестера отправились посмотреть на Sex Pistols. Впечатлившись, они организовали группу Joy Division. Через три года это был вопрос искусства, жизни и смерти. Сегодня, тридцать лет спустя, у Joy Division как никогда, — и поклонников, и влияния, благодаря мощному наследию, которое резко резонирует в сегодняшней предельно карьеристской музыкальной индустрии и искусственно выращиваемой поп-культуре."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"欢乐分裂","runtime":93,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"加拿大2007年9月7日（多伦多电影节）"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"조이 디비전","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"98년 라디오 헤드의 투어를 담은 음악다큐로 이름을 알린 그랜트 지 감독이 이번에는 조이 디비전의 음악을 담아냈다. 단조롭고 건조한 멜로디와 시니컬하고 염세적인 가사, 몽환적인 효과음이 어우러진 음악으로 사랑받았던 영국 출신 록밴드 조이 디비전은 1980년 보컬 이안 커티스가 23세에 자살하며 단 두 장의 음반을 내고 사라지게 된다. 살아있는 멤버들의 인터뷰와 과거 영상은 감각적인 영상 편집으로 오버랩되고, 무엇보다도 풍부한 공연 실황과 음악이 영화를 가득 채운다.  조이 디비전은 2차 세계대전을 배경으로 한 소설『인형의 집』에 등장하는 단어로 매춘 장소를 뜻하는 속어지만, 음악팬들에 게는 맨체스터 신을 널리 알린 고딕 록 그룹으로 더 잘 알려져 있다. 그런가하면 영화 팬들에게는 의 사운드트랙으로, 또 스물넷의 나이로 요절한 보컬 이언 커티스의 삶을 다룬 영화 로도 알려져 있다. 그룹 조이 디비전은 1977년 결성되어 이언 커티스가 세상을 떠난 1980년까지 단 두 장의 음반만을 내놓았지만, 그들이 음악계에 남긴 파문은 아직까지도 길게 드리워져 있다. 그랜트 지 감독은 다큐멘터리 을 통해 비록 짧았지만 너무나 강렬했던 이들의 궤적을 돌아보고 있다. 이들의 근거지였던 맨체스터의 공연장 일렉트릭 서커스와 음반을 만들었던 팩토리 레코드, 그리고 TV에 출연했을 때와 공연 기록 영상들이 이제는 뉴 오더라는 그룹으로 활동하고 있는 살아남은 세 멤버들의 생생한 회상과 함께 펼쳐진다. 은행에서 돈을 빌려 첫 음반을 녹음한 일부터 충격적이었던 이언 커티스의 자살에 이르기까지 짧았지만 굵게 활동했던 조이 디비전의 전설을 만나게 된다. 특히 커트 코베인이“세상에서 가장 암울한 러브송”이라고 했던 명곡‘Love Will Tear Us Apart’가 흐르는 장면에서는 짙은 감동에 휩싸이게 된다. (전진수)"},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Chronologický popis vlivné anglické rockové skupiny z konce 70. let."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"歡樂分裂","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"加拿大 2007 年 9 月 7 日（多倫多電影節）"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"54f36ad8c3a3681b71002738","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/54f36ad8c3a3681b71002738","author":"John Chard","content":"$11","created_at":"2015-03-01T19:39:04.659Z","updated_at":"2024-05-16T15:22:08.476Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":8,"username":"John Chard","avatar_path":"/utEXl2EDiXBK6f41wCLsvprvMg4.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":5708,"adult":false,"title":"Control","video":false,"overview":"The story of Joy Division’s lead singer Ian Curtis, from his schoolboy days in 1973 to his suicide on the eve of the band's first American tour in 1980.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0252,"vote_count":911,"poster_path":"/jOJiaOhwrDdwqTRZvZOhbndqHGp.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-12","vote_average":7.516,"backdrop_path":"/dwxdn3ppDAn7QtaLlhGDEErWfg9.jpg","original_title":"Control","original_language":"en"},{"id":31132,"adult":false,"title":"Killer","video":false,"overview":"An innocent cab driver is mistaken for a contract killer and imprisoned. Soon, he is sprung by a mob boss who needs a \"killer\" for a few more jobs.","genre_ids":[35,28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.344,"vote_count":168,"poster_path":"/ho08qS2vBVFywB4I180PhaTtxg4.jpg","release_date":"1997-11-17","vote_average":7.622,"backdrop_path":"/vmGWKadwri2y67t4truG1nPVd6v.jpg","original_title":"Kiler","original_language":"pl"},{"id":2750,"adult":false,"title":"24 Hour Party People","video":false,"overview":"Manchester, 1976. Tony Wilson is an ambitious but frustrated local TV news reporter looking for a way to make his mark. After witnessing a life-changing concert by a band known as the Sex Pistols, he persuades his station to televise one of their performances, and soon Manchester's punk groups are clamoring for him to manage them. Riding the wave of a musical revolution, Wilson and his friends create the legendary Factory Records label and The Hacienda club.","genre_ids":[35,18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7515,"vote_count":504,"poster_path":"/8f50NQ1wz6hdxfCISCPV8XQ6DII.jpg","release_date":"2002-02-13","vote_average":6.96,"backdrop_path":"/ucRD8UUr5tllltg3ZTWoXOyPXyJ.jpg","original_title":"24 Hour Party People","original_language":"en"},{"id":412924,"adult":false,"title":"Supersonic","video":false,"overview":"Supersonic charts the meteoric rise of Oasis from the council estates of Manchester to some of the biggest concerts of all time in just three short years.  This palpable, raw and moving film shines a light on one of the most genre and generation-defining British bands that has ever existed and features candid new interviews with Noel and Liam Gallagher, their mother, and members of the band and road crew.","genre_ids":[10402,99,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5727,"vote_count":233,"poster_path":"/gMHLEKTB22J212To1gSnundcIhH.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-02","vote_average":7.384,"backdrop_path":"/bbDMy8ou6N8yL5VidQpzo6kZZVk.jpg","original_title":"Supersonic","original_language":"en"},{"id":32151,"adult":false,"title":"Triangle","video":false,"overview":"Life has not been kind to drinking buddies Sam, Fai, and Mok as they struggle to make ends meet, until one stormy evening when a mysterious old man appears before them in a bar with a 'get rich quick' scheme: an ancient treasure buried under a high-security government building.","genre_ids":[53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1521,"vote_count":62,"poster_path":"/2BhKMrlbuwTbaQZAvxRLF7FF7kE.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-01","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/jzt28N70y6LJ3chW618Z5tdS8FA.jpg","original_title":"鐵三角","original_language":"cn"},{"id":381427,"adult":false,"title":"Rocky Mountain Express","video":false,"overview":"A history of the nation's first transcontinental railway accompanies a steam-train ride through the Canadian Rockies.","genre_ids":[99,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1075,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/ylDsWwvE431ZGPi9NklDCxddqnA.jpg","release_date":"2011-09-30","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/uDTjbkcmfW6Q8Ne26Swi83jlVJV.jpg","original_title":"Rocky Mountain Express","original_language":"en"},{"id":1003744,"adult":false,"title":"Tenochtitlan, capitale de l'empire Azteque","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/nUgNMiis1oGJMXbhHDOZYOrIYLH.jpg","release_date":"2022-06-30","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/f3ks2QNWt8Kbv7loYrbHXPGo2JN.jpg","original_title":"Tenochtitlan, capitale de l'empire Azteque","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1124,"adult":false,"title":"The Prestige","video":false,"overview":"A mysterious story of two magicians whose intense rivalry leads them on a life-long battle for supremacy -- full of obsession, deceit and jealousy with dangerous and deadly consequences.","genre_ids":[18,9648,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.8952,"vote_count":17251,"poster_path":"/Ag2B2KHKQPukjH7WutmgnnSNurZ.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-17","vote_average":8.205,"backdrop_path":"/qc9zR02j2apoEwMdptMYBoAFYUC.jpg","original_title":"The Prestige","original_language":"en"},{"id":603,"adult":false,"title":"The Matrix","video":false,"overview":"Set in the 22nd century, The Matrix tells the story of a computer hacker who joins a group of underground insurgents fighting the vast and powerful computers who now rule the earth.","genre_ids":[28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.54,"vote_count":27421,"poster_path":"/p96dm7sCMn4VYAStA6siNz30G1r.jpg","release_date":"1999-03-31","vote_average":8.238,"backdrop_path":"/tlm8UkiQsitc8rSuIAscQDCnP8d.jpg","original_title":"The Matrix","original_language":"en"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.7563,"vote_count":11389,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":262903,"adult":false,"title":"Main Tera Hero","video":false,"overview":"Seenu loves Sunaina but they're chased by a stalking cop, an infatuated beauty and her mafia don dad - can Seenu's heroics work?","genre_ids":[10749,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5111,"vote_count":192,"poster_path":"/bupZH3i1SAaLLC0OgYMSLDZN63Q.jpg","release_date":"2014-04-04","vote_average":5.667,"backdrop_path":"/wgYx4MwezeoAkRVAJsYdOMAMeWC.jpg","original_title":"मैं तेरा हीरो","original_language":"hi"},{"id":38360,"adult":false,"title":"The Cranes Are Flying","video":false,"overview":"Veronika and Boris come together in Moscow shortly before World War II. Walking along the river, they watch cranes fly overhead, and promise to rendezvous before Boris leaves to fight. Boris misses the meeting and is off to the front lines, while Veronika waits patiently, sending letters faithfully. After her house is bombed, Veronika moves in with Boris' family, into the company of a cousin with his own intentions.","genre_ids":[18,10749,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9992,"vote_count":439,"poster_path":"/foXYOdXEJ0rvtTDo4LLnsUnvPLB.jpg","release_date":"1957-10-12","vote_average":7.916,"backdrop_path":"/kmmt99iuCEm8iX39yxfqKu5xHGj.jpg","original_title":"Летят журавли","original_language":"ru"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4022,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.7588,"vote_count":14042,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":680,"adult":false,"title":"Pulp Fiction","video":false,"overview":"A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster's moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.","genre_ids":[53,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.3091,"vote_count":29739,"poster_path":"/vQWk5YBFWF4bZaofAbv0tShwBvQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-10","vote_average":8.486,"backdrop_path":"/96hiUXEuYsu4tcnvlaY8tEMFM0m.jpg","original_title":"Pulp Fiction","original_language":"en"},{"id":551332,"adult":false,"title":"The Two Popes","video":false,"overview":"Frustrated with the direction of the church, Cardinal Bergoglio requests permission to retire in 2012 from Pope Benedict. Instead, facing scandal and self-doubt, the introspective Pope Benedict summons his harshest critic and future successor to Rome to reveal a secret that would shake the foundations of the Catholic Church.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.406,"vote_count":3098,"poster_path":"/4d4mTSfDIFIbUbMLUfaKodvxYXA.jpg","release_date":"2019-11-27","vote_average":7.491,"backdrop_path":"/bOPessdyd0dChHy70FM8Om7CgDg.jpg","original_title":"The Two Popes","original_language":"en"},{"id":466272,"adult":false,"title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","video":false,"overview":"Los Angeles, 1969. TV star Rick Dalton, a struggling actor specializing in westerns, and stuntman Cliff Booth, his best friend, try to survive in a constantly changing movie industry. Dalton is the neighbor of the young and promising actress and model Sharon Tate, who has just married the prestigious Polish director Roman Polanski…","genre_ids":[35,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.721,"vote_count":14579,"poster_path":"/8j58iEBw9pOXFD2L0nt0ZXeHviB.jpg","release_date":"2019-07-24","vote_average":7.423,"backdrop_path":"/kKTPv9LKKs5L3oO1y5FNObxAPWI.jpg","original_title":"Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood","original_language":"en"},{"id":496243,"adult":false,"title":"Parasite","video":false,"overview":"All unemployed, Ki-taek's family takes peculiar interest in the wealthy and glamorous Parks for their livelihood until they get entangled in an unexpected incident.","genre_ids":[35,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":29.2527,"vote_count":20185,"poster_path":"/7IiTTgloJzvGI1TAYymCfbfl3vT.jpg","release_date":"2019-05-30","vote_average":8.493,"backdrop_path":"/hiKmpZMGZsrkA3cdce8a7Dpos1j.jpg","original_title":"기생충","original_language":"ko"},{"id":475557,"adult":false,"title":"Joker","video":false,"overview":"During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.","genre_ids":[80,53,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.0422,"vote_count":27338,"poster_path":"/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-01","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/hO7KbdvGOtDdeg0W4Y5nKEHeDDh.jpg","original_title":"Joker","original_language":"en"},{"id":27205,"adult":false,"title":"Inception","video":false,"overview":"Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating the subconscious of his targets is offered a chance to regain his old life as payment for a task considered to be impossible: \"inception\", the implantation of another person's idea into a target's subconscious.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":27.2486,"vote_count":38743,"poster_path":"/xlaY2zyzMfkhk0HSC5VUwzoZPU1.jpg","release_date":"2010-07-15","vote_average":8.371,"backdrop_path":"/8ZTVqvKDQ8emSGUEMjsS4yHAwrp.jpg","original_title":"Inception","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":5708,"adult":false,"title":"Control","video":false,"overview":"The story of Joy Division’s lead singer Ian Curtis, from his schoolboy days in 1973 to his suicide on the eve of the band's first American tour in 1980.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.0252,"vote_count":911,"poster_path":"/jOJiaOhwrDdwqTRZvZOhbndqHGp.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-12","vote_average":7.516,"backdrop_path":"/dwxdn3ppDAn7QtaLlhGDEErWfg9.jpg","original_title":"Control","original_language":"en"},{"id":1358533,"adult":false,"title":"Ossessione","video":false,"overview":"Two Italian brothers, Franco and Giovanni, are marked by envy and resentment. While Giovanni, a talented painter, gains recognition in Brazil, Franco stays in Italy, enjoying the attention of their parents —attention that was always denied to the younger brother. When Franco asks Giovanni for a painting during a brief trip to Brazil, the bitterness between them reaches a breaking point, revealing a truth as painful as the artwork created.","genre_ids":[53,9648],"popularity":0.1164,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/qSK6lqkDIYyQpGyIrH6tVJRJp55.jpg","release_date":"2024-06-22","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":"/6u7ymDvGG892jaztt424mNHJ1wB.jpg","original_title":"Ossessione","original_language":"pt"},{"id":470675,"adult":false,"title":"David Hockney at the Royal Academy of Arts","video":true,"overview":"Widely considered Britain’s most popular artist, David Hockney is a global sensation with exhibitions in London, New York, Paris and beyond, attracting millions of visitors worldwide.  Now entering his 9th decade, Hockney shows absolutely no evidence of slowing down or losing his trademark boldness.  Featuring intimate and in-depth interviews with Hockney, this revealing film focuses on two blockbuster exhibitions held in 2012 and 2016 at the Royal Academy of Art in London.  Director Phil Grabsky secured privileged access to craft this cinematic celebration of a 21st century master of creativity.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.1389,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/v255UybnLiZ7sHeQtSVDTkLW9bF.jpg","release_date":"2017-11-21","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/xuOh9Spzr3ehPAdM1SIiLogRHiC.jpg","original_title":"David Hockney at the Royal Academy of Arts","original_language":"en"},{"id":470677,"adult":false,"title":"Cézanne: Portraits of a Life","video":true,"overview":"Dedicated to the portrait work of Paul Cézanne, the exhibition opens in Paris before traveling to London and Washington.  One cannot appreciate 20th century art without understanding the significance and genius of Paul Cézanne. Filmed at the National Portrait Gallery in London, with additional interviews from experts and curators from MoMA in New York, National Gallery of Art in Washington DC, and Musée d’Orsay in Paris, and correspondence from the artist himself, the film takes audiences to the places Cézanne lived and worked and sheds light on an artist who is perhaps one of the least known and yet most important of all the Impressionists.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.1338,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/3sJsoYF9wT6PQpJd4WURoppUp5B.jpg","release_date":"2018-01-23","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/eWgNqM2r2gQCLwCdrZTvM0R25bV.jpg","original_title":"Cézanne: Portraits of a Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":1066923,"adult":false,"title":"Dream Big: A Big Gigantic Story","video":false,"overview":"It’s been a long road for saxophonist/producer Dominic Lalli and drummer Jeremy Salken to “ROWDYTOWN IV,” the fourth installment of their massive hometown experience.  Their journey is beautifully captured in this documentary short  film which chronicles the duo’s history and how they broke saxophone into dance music alongside a compelling behind the scenes look at producing the Rowdytown show.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.1739,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/vxIV1u1gvCaNtPbbcUb4uyGKtnM.jpg","release_date":"2015-09-25","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Dream Big: A Big Gigantic Story","original_language":"en"},{"id":661271,"adult":false,"title":"The Homosexuals","video":false,"overview":"On March 7, 1967, 40 million Americans tuned in to watch CBS Reports: The Homosexuals, network television’s first documentary on homosexuality. Near the top of the program, host and interviewer Mike Wallace calls homosexuals “the most despised minority in the United States.” The hour that follows is filled with salacious location footage, sermonizing therapists, and shadowed interviews with distraught homosexuals.","genre_ids":[99,10770],"popularity":0.8481,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/qvTFzSryyy2OdUYt0DnmFECAD1q.jpg","release_date":"1967-03-07","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":"/zMDfSDW6n5dyoVdZA9Bswc7aRy0.jpg","original_title":"The Homosexuals","original_language":"en"},{"id":661286,"adult":false,"title":"The Summers of It – Chapter One: You'll Float Too","video":false,"overview":"This documentary focuses on the actors and their journey over two summers to create the remake to the original IT, by Stephen King. The documentary originally released as bonus material, bundled with IT: Chapter Two.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":1.8752,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/awFM888QgS0PB3SZXMD5HikNXNQ.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-10","vote_average":8.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The Summers of It – Chapter One: You'll Float Too","original_language":"en"},{"id":661289,"adult":false,"title":"The Summers of It - Chapter Two: It Ends","video":false,"overview":"This documentary focuses on the actors and their journey over two summers to create the remake to the original IT, by Stephen King. The documentary originally released as bonus material, bundled with IT: Chapter Two.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":1.4959,"vote_count":66,"poster_path":"/oXtw9zyoRtt1PiF6MSBNpSYSHRu.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-10","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/nXXhswchGwLP13zj5C2f8PA3X3P.jpg","original_title":"The Summers of It - Chapter Two: It Ends","original_language":"en"},{"id":1066946,"adult":false,"title":"Aikatsu! 10th Story: Starway to the Future","video":false,"overview":"While Akari is shining brightly as Starlight Queen, the duo unit \"Cosmos\", composed of Ichigo and Akari, just had a successful first live event!  As time flows by while their activites continue, Ichigo, who is now in her third year of Starlight School's high school divison, is starting to become aware of her graduation that is coming in half a year. She knows that even after she graduates, she'd like to continue her idol activities. However, to pass the hurdle towards her graduation, there is one more fork in the road lying ahead. As idols, for Ichigo, Aoi and Ran, exactly what path would they like to move forward on from now on, this important decision is now something they must consider with care.","genre_ids":[16,35,18,10402],"popularity":0.4868,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/cF0j6lV6mjZHfixWjB7KTvq393M.jpg","release_date":"2023-01-20","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/vx4CPLT6m5NSrkeozbnP7vcYWt1.jpg","original_title":"アイカツ! 10th STORY ～未来へのSTARWAY～","original_language":"ja"},{"id":861054,"adult":false,"title":"The Beatles: In Japan (7/1/1966)","video":false,"overview":"The second of two concerts, where the boys have grey suits, was video taped by Nippon Television. The two shows were edited together and broadcast during The Beatles Recital, From Nippon Budokan, Tokyo, which was screened on NTV Channel 4 on 1 July from 9pm.","genre_ids":[10402,99],"popularity":0.2412,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/qvANDWJ8rvTjqsNZ3K1Y0Mlyc38.jpg","release_date":"1966-07-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/jF60zm5zq15kooW4E3jEYxlVQ0R.jpg","original_title":"ビートルズ・イン・ジャパン","original_language":"en"},{"id":861066,"adult":false,"title":"Santa Barbara","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by the 1980s American soap opera, Santa Barbara, Svetlana became a mail-order bride from post-Soviet Russia to America. She took her two children with her to California to meet a stranger, a man who would soon become her husband and father to her children. The film brings together the audition process, behind- the-scenes footage, archival home movies, scripted scenes, and an interview with the director's mother, Svetlana. This project is an immersive form of visual storytelling that employs memory and performance in equal measure to show the journey of immigrating to America.","genre_ids":[99,18,10749],"popularity":0.8883,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/fWSMjrZBX3x3Y9gUVjz2vErkynI.jpg","release_date":"2022-06-10","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Santa Barbara","original_language":"ru"},{"id":1459010,"adult":false,"title":"I Took My Avocado to Aspen, Colorado","video":false,"overview":"A \"mobbed up\" gopher treats his avocado associate to a lavish weekend of private planes, fancy hotels and expensive gifts, lulling the unsuspecting fruit into a blissful stupor, before tossing him off a high-rise balcony. This animated evolution of a film-within-a-film is a stop-motion journey filled with danger, intrigue and rhymes.","genre_ids":[16,35,80,10402],"popularity":0.1637,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/t4qWbS5AERWcjthNGXZ4UaJckhy.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"I Took My Avocado to Aspen, Colorado","original_language":"en"},{"id":661321,"adult":false,"title":"Circus Maximus","video":false,"overview":"A story of a circus in decline which is approaching its imminent end.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"popularity":1.7899,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2015-12-31","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Circus Maximus","original_language":"pl"},{"id":861094,"adult":false,"title":"My Leftover Ladies","video":false,"overview":"Meet four Taiwanese women, the actual \"leftover ladies\" fighting to stay breathing in a somewhat stifling society. Since 2012, their friend in common, Chou Tung-yen, has been \"stalking\" them, capturing on film moments of these women's daily lives.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.1254,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5VLOxXGivypvWr9lj5MZEsh3mmI.jpg","release_date":"2015-03-17","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"剩女，真的？","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1258901,"adult":false,"title":"Electric Callboy: Tekkno - Live in Europe","video":false,"overview":"A compilation of live performances from across Europe by the German electronicore band, Electric Callboy.","genre_ids":[10402,99],"popularity":0.1457,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/tUGOa09hpFqpjIrc8RkyJ10QQCo.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-20","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Electric Callboy: Tekkno - Live in Europe","original_language":"de"},{"id":470763,"adult":false,"title":"Vegan: Everyday Stories","video":false,"overview":"A feature-length documentary that explores the lives of four remarkably different people who share a common thread - they're all vegan. The movie traces the personal journeys of an ultramarathon runner who has overcome addiction to compete in one hundred mile races, a cattle rancher's wife who creates the first cattle ranch turned farmed animal sanctuary in Texas, a food truck owner cooking up knee-buckling plant-based foods, and an 8-year-old girl who convinces her family of six to go vegan.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.1995,"vote_count":7,"poster_path":"/weKSU3Ah0FiFmLVqmqsPZgtryBi.jpg","release_date":"2016-06-04","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/4xLiCGTCRt74o5sJfS6JdI2bnyh.jpg","original_title":"Vegan: Everyday Stories","original_language":"en"},{"id":470768,"adult":false,"title":"A World War II Fairy Tale: The Making of Michael Mann's 'The Keep'","video":false,"overview":"Exploring Michael Mann's 1983 film adapted from the F. Paul Wilson novel and its impact.","genre_ids":[99],"popularity":0.3032,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/hn9zh5cvq48tJQsphydK5lABN0j.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-10","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/waD3cbSrQ0nUfEei430HpYNAECe.jpg","original_title":"A World War II Fairy Tale: The Making of Michael Mann's 'The Keep'","original_language":"en"},{"id":277499,"adult":false,"title":"From Star Wars to Star Wars: The Story of Industrial Light & Magic","video":false,"overview":"The incredible evolution of George Lucas' special effects dream 